<h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
<h3>
  You have requested for password reset of your account on geethub. Please
  proceed to your task by clicking the following Reset Password button.
</h3>
<table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td style="border-radius: 2px;" bgcolor="#3D85A3">
            <a
              href="{{currentUrl}}reset-password/{{_id}}/{{uniqueString}}"
              target="_blank"
              style="padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid #3D85A3;border-radius: 2px;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px; color: #ffffff;text-decoration: none;font-weight:bold;display: inline-block;"
            >
              Reset Password
            </a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<p>This Link will expires in 1 hour</p>
<hr />
<p>If you have problems, please paste the below URL into your web browser.</p>
<p>{{currentUrl}}reset-password/{{_id}}/{{uniqueString}}</p>
<hr />
<p>Thanks! Geethub team</p>